<p>I have a Clojure vector containing hashmaps.  These hashmaps are not associated with any key themselves. But <em>all</em> of these hashmaps have a common key â€” lets say <code>"ckey"</code>.  I want to extract the those hashmaps whose <code>"ckey"</code> has the value <code>"test"</code>.</p>  <p>The data is actually a parsed json. Something like this:-</p>  <pre><code>testdata :{ sample1 : "samplevalue1" sample2 : "samplevalue2" sample3 : {innersample3 : "innersamplevalue3"} sample4 : "samplevalue4" sample5 : [{moresample []             link {innersample5 : "innersamplevalue5"}             ckeydata [{ckey:"test" something: somethingValue something2: somethingValue2}]}          {moresample []             link {innersample5 : "innersamplevalue5"}             ckeydata [{ckey:"test1"something: somethingValue something2: somethingValue2}]}          {moresample []             link {innersample5 : "innersamplevalue5"}             ckeydata [ {ckey:"test2" something: somethingValue something2: somethingValue2}]}          {moresample []             link {innersample5 : "innersamplevalue5"}             ckeydata [ {ckey:"test" something: somethingValue something2: somethingValue2}]}]} </code></pre>  <p>So in this case I want to extract hashmaps from <code>sample5</code> whose <code>"ckeydata"</code> key has a vector which contains a hashmap having a <code>"ckey"</code> value of <code>"test"</code>.</p>  <p>The data in Clojure format:</p>  <pre><code>testdata {     :sample1  "samplevalue1"     :sample2  "samplevalue2"     :sample3  {:innersample3  "innersamplevalue3"}     :sample4  "samplevalue4"     :sample5  [{:moresample []                 :link {innersample5  "innersamplevalue5"}                 :ckeydata [{:ckey:"test" :something: somethingValue something2 somethingValue2}]}                {:moresample []                  :link {innersample5  "innersamplevalue5"}                  :ckeydata [{:ckey "test1" :something "somethingValue" :something2 "somethingValue2"}]}                {:moresample []                  :link {:innersample5  "innersamplevalue5"}                  :ckeydata [ {:ckey "test2" :something "somethingValue" :something2 "somethingValue2"}]}                {:moresample []                  :link {innersample5 : "innersamplevalue5"}                  :ckeydata [ {:ckey "test" :something  "somethingValue" :something2 "somethingValue2"}]}]} </code></pre>  <p>Note:  I don't want to use many filters and keep looping through the code.</p>